messages.messageBody:
I know many of you are in touch with Valerie but for those who might not
have heard, she was able to go see her house in Lake Charles and was
please that the damage isn't too extensive.
They're still asking people not to move back in to Lake Charles but I
think she plans to visit frequently to get things in order. She's
staying in Baton Rouge for the time being.

Deb Lewis
